# Phase 01 — Types Extraction

**Priority**: Critical (blocks all other phases)
**Status**: Pending
**Effort**: ~1h

---

## Context Links

- Source: [src/store/useAppStore.ts](../../src/store/useAppStore.ts) (lines 1–120, all type definitions)
