## Vendored Packages (libs/)

Dự án vendor 2 private packages để tránh network timeout khi deploy lên Vercel:

1. **@frontend-team/tiptap-kit** (v0.2.7)
2. **@frontend-team/ui-kit** (v1.1.1)

